Dear Anmol , 



Thank you very much for posting your Content Writing internship requirement on Internshala.



Please note that you have posted an unpaid internship. On Internshala we allow only paid internships, except in case of NGOs/NPOs & niche profiles (Law, Experimental Physics, Library Science, and the likes).



Your internship will be reviewed and approved only after you confirm the following:

     If you're an NGO/NPO, please confirm. 
     If you wish to make it a paid internship, please update the stipend here (the minimum assured stipend allowed on Internshala is Rs.2000/month for an in-office internship and Rs.1000/month for a work from home internship).

Kindly let me know for any further queries.


